code: @Override protected boolean isExtensionExposed(Object extensionBean) {     if (isHealthEndpointExtension(extensionBean) && !isCloudFoundryHealthEndpointExtension(extensionBean)) {         // Filter regular health endpoint extensions so a CF version can replace them         return false.     }     return true. }

private boolean isHealthEndpointExtension(Object extensionBean) {     AnnotationAttributes attributes = AnnotatedElementUtils.getMergedAnnotationAttributes(extensionBean.getClass(), EndpointWebExtension.class).     Class<?> endpoint = (attributes != null) ? attributes.getClass("endpoint") : null.     return (endpoint != null && HealthEndpoint.class.isAssignableFrom(endpoint)). }
